          <title>
            <string language="en">Peptide bond formed between two amino acids</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Peptidbindung bildete sich zwischen zwei 
Aminosäuren</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Obligation de peptide formée entre deux acides 
aminés</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A ligação do peptide deu forma entre dois 
aminos-ácido</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il legame del peptide ha formato fra due 
amminoacidi</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Δεσμός πεπτιδίων που διαμορφώνεται μεταξύ δύο 
αμινοξέων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El enlace del peptide formó entre dos 
aminoácidos</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the (a) planar structure, (b) the delocalised pi orbitals, and (c) the bond angles  of the peptide bond formed between two amino acids.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <structure>
            <source>structureValues</source>
            <value>atomic</value>
          </structure>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die (a) planare Struktur, 
(b) delocalised PU Orbitals, und (c) bildeten sich die Bondwinkel der 
Peptidbindung zwischen zwei Aminosäuren.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre (a) la structure 
planaire, (b) delocalised des orbitales de pi, et (c) les angles 
d'obligation de l'obligation de peptide ont formé entre deux acides
aminés.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra (a) a estrutura planar, 
(b) delocalised orbitals do pi, e (c) os ângulos bond da ligação do
peptide deram forma entre dois aminos-ácido.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra (a) la struttura 
planare, (b) delocalised i orbitals di pi e (c) gli angoli schiavi del
legame del peptide hanno formato fra due amminoacidi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει (α) επίπεδη δομή, (β) τα 
τροχιακοοι pi, και (γ) οι γωνίες δεσμών του πεπτιδίου συνδέουν 
διαμορφωμένος μεταξύ δύο αμινοξέων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra (a) la estructura 
planar, (b) delocalised orbitarios del pi, y (c) los ángulos en 
enlace del enlace del peptide formaron entre dos aminoácidos.</string>
          </description>
